reviews.review_text: 10-2-87 Well played show. Nice sounding remaster by Charlie. A little tape hiss in the quiet parts if that bothers you.

'Twas '89 Jerry, Phil and Bobby are on for the whole show. The soundboard shenanigans don't intrude too much.
Sweet 2nd set.
Thanks for the excellent xfer Charlie!

There must be some kind of way out of here Not bad sound as 87 goes..Let it Grow is splendid~!! Interesting placement of Don't Ease..Solid Show but nothing to crazy..Give It A Whirl>Forever Grateful>Forever Dead~!!
